                        Program Details
                    </h3>
                    <p>Our online and hybrid medical assistant training program is designed to provide comprehensive,
                        hands-on instruction that prepares you for a successful career in medical assisting. Upon
                        completing this program, students will demonstrate the following core competencies:</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clinicalCompetenceOHSecPC sectionGap">
                <div class="backgroundCenterImage"></div>

                <div class="row g-5">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="POnlinePBox">
                            <div class="POnlinePBoxContent">
                                <div class="POnlinePBoxHead">
                                    <h3>Online Program</h3>
                                    <p>The Online Only learning path provides full flexibility, allowing you to complete
                                        all coursework and assignments online.
                                        You will have access to the same comprehensive curriculum, including clinical
                                        and administrative training, patient care education, and exam preparation
                                        materials. However, the hands-on clinical experience will be simulated through
                                        virtual labs, and you will be expected to complete clinical hours at an approved
                                        local healthcare facility.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="POnlinePBoxFeatures">
                                    <h3>Key Features of Online Only</h3>
                                    <ol class="POnlinePBoxFeatures">
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">1</div><span>Complete Online Flexibility: Study at
                                                your own pace, on your own schedule.</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">2</div><span>Virtual Labs: Engage in simulated
                                                clinical tasks through interactive software.</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">3</div><span>Local Clinical Experience:
                                                Complete required clinical hours at a healthcare facility near
                                                you.</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">4</div><span>Online Support: Access to instructors and
                                                peers via virtual platforms for assistance and collaboration.</span>
                                        </li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <img src="assets/images/home/learnmore-bg2.svg" alt="Hybrid program illustration"
                                class="bg-shape Hybridillustration" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="POnlinePBox PhybridPBox">
                            <div class="POnlinePBoxContent">
                                <div class="POnlinePBoxHead">
                                    <h3>Hybrid Program:</h3>
                                    <p>The Hybrid learning path blends the flexibility of online learning with
                                        in-person, hands-on training. In addition to the online coursework, you will
                                        attend in-person training sessions at our Arizona campus (two on-campus classes per week) for clinical practice
                                        and skill-building workshops. This allows you to gain real-world experience
                                        while still enjoying the flexibility of online learning for theoretical
                                        subjects.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="POnlinePBoxFeatures">
                                    <h3>Key Features of Hybrid</h3>
                                    <ol class="POnlinePBoxFeatures">
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">1</div><span>Combination of Online Learning &
                                                In-Person Training: Learn theory online while gaining practical
                                                experience in person.</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">2</div><span>Hands-On Clinical Training: Participate
                                                in face-to-face clinical labs, ensuring you develop essential skills
                                                with direct guidance from instructors.</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">3</div><span>Flexible Schedule: Manage your coursework
                                                online while attending in-person clinical sessions as required.</span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="boxCount">4</div><span>Instructor-Led Workshops: Engage in
                                                workshops for personalised learning and skill development.</span>
                                        </li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <img src="assets/images/home/learnmore-bg2.svg" alt="Hybrid program illustration"
                                class="bg-shape Hybridillustration" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


